      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/us/politics/the-docket-roberts-voting-rights.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从他作为律师的早期和担任法官的最初几年起，首席大法官就一直致力于限制《投票权法》的效力。]]></description>
