    <item>
      <title>农作物少计引发人们对美国农业部可靠性的质疑数据</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/business/usda-farmers-crops-data.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年玉米种植面积预计减少了 450 万英亩。农业部表示，导致这一失误的原因是缺乏调查回应，而不是裁员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/business/usda-farmers-crops-data.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 15:22:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
