    <item>
      <title>特朗普可能从德国撤军。这并不像以前那么可怕。</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/world/europe/trump-germany-troops-merz-threat.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国大幅增加了军费开支，旨在减少对华盛顿的依赖。它对美国袭击伊朗的支持也可能为其带来影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/30/world/europe/trump-germany-troops-merz-threat.html</guid>
